high_descs: Turn left, go forward, then turn left to face the toilet.
Pick up the rag on the back of the toilet.
Turn left and go to the sink in front of you.
Wash the rag in the sink.
Turn around, and then turn back around to face the drawers under the sink, to the right.
Put the rag in the top drawer on the right
anns.task_desc: Put a clean rag in the drawer.

high_descs: Move to the toilet to the left of the shower
Pick up a rag from the toilet
Move to the sink to the left of you
Clean the rag in the sink and pick it up
Move to the counter to the right of you
Put the rag in the drawer and close it
anns.task_desc: Put a clean rag in the drawer under the sink on the right.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the wall, then turn left to face the toilet.
Pick up the dirty red rag off of the toilet tank.
Turn left and walk around the toilet to the sink.
Put the dirty red rag in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean red rag.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and take a step, then turn left again to face the counter.
Open the top right drawer of the counter and put the clean red rag inside on the left, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean red rag in a drawer.
